30 March 2014 Members of the media are invited to a post State of Nation Address (SoNA) media briefing on peacekeeping and post conflict reconstruction and development efforts by South Africa.The Minister of Defence, Ms Nosiviwe Mapisa-Nqakula will lead the media briefing.Details are as follows: Date: Monday, 31 March 2014 Time: 14h00 (note change of time) Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, Cape Town, Parliament NB: There will be a video-link to GCIS Press Room, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard, Corner Festival Street, Hatfield, PretoriaRSVP: Ireen Magwai (Pretoria) Cell: 072 822 5869 E-mail:ireen@gcis.gov.za Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) Cell: 076 904 3557 E-mail: mzi@gcis.gov.zaEnquiries: Nikelwa Tengimfene Cell: 082 574 5495Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)